830
01:00:32,590 --> 01:00:36,580
Mr. Minister, if you'll forgive me.
This all sound excellent,

831
01:00:36,750 --> 01:00:38,700
and we will return to it, but...

832
01:00:38,750 --> 01:00:41,700
if you'll indulge me for just one
more minute---

833
01:00:42,340 --> 01:00:47,330
<i>Well. Soccer is usually their favorite
sport here. But things changed today.</i>

834
01:00:47,670 --> 01:00:52,170
<i>When a group of local kids really took to
the Springboks in a surprise visit...</i>

835
01:00:52,410 --> 01:00:54,240
<i>...Francois Pienaar...</i>

836
01:00:54,330 --> 01:00:55,590
You see that,

837
01:00:56,250 --> 01:00:59,050
that picture is worth any number of
speeches.

